La Collection Privée Christian Dior bottles can now be adorned with the iconic motifs of the House. The personalization atelier offers a selection of fifteen carefully crafted couture caps celebrating the original spirit of the couturier-perfumer. The ultimate couture touch to dress your fragrance in Dior.
 
*Available for 100ml and 200ml formats. The couture caps are sold separately; bottles come with their original cap.
